node.text: @adbphotoinc @kobemural and I have been working on a project for quite some time now. If you have any murals or art tributes of Kobe and Gigi, please send them to @kobemural for my consideration in our new project. Can’t wait to see what you got! 💜 btw, I am NOT working with any other tribute projects. This is the ONLY Kobe and Gigi art inspired project I am personally involved in. Thanks for the love. Xo, VB 💜💛
